Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.11,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}何も怖くなんてないさ 　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.65,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}手にしたものを失うくらい  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:52.73,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}争いを待つ事を繰り返して  かすめて  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:56.27,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}何もかもを欲しがっていた  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:59.72,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}迷えるものの誓い   
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:05.19,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}未だ見ぬ世界を創りだす事  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.48,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}朽ち果てていく   
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:15.52,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}哀しい夢を遮るものは  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.38,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}自らの闇だって   
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.82,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\rOPcn}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:26.12,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\rOPcn}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.28,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\rOPcn}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:31.50,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\rOPcn}Makes me feel{\r}  何処からか  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.88,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}流れる景色変わらなくなって  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.57,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}音もなく解き放つ   
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.45,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}畏れ断ち切り何時からか   
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.20,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}高鳴る鼓動止まらなくなって  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:52.61,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}易しくも消し去って    
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.11,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}没有什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.65,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}哪怕失去已经得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:52.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}不断等待着争斗  却又瞒天过海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:56.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}想要得到所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:59.72,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是迷茫之人的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:05.19,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}想要创造出未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.48,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}此志不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:15.52,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}遮掩梦之忧伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.38,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}是自身的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.82,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:26.12,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:31.50,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Makes me feel  不知从何处来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.88,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}眼前的景色不再变化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.57,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}悄无声息地释放着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}不知何时起  已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.20,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}砰然鼓噪的心跳无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:52.61,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}就如此轻易地  消散殆尽

